esting) and", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841713, "box": [146.41967996031744, 81.03777059712763, 732.161063095238, 119.56704799697661], "id_box_line": 4, "box_line": [146.42576284722222, 159.1330551776266, 732.142818501984, 21.948000377928906], "text": "another production Kubernetes cluster to represent performance testing and produc\u2010", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841713, "box": [146.41967996031744, 81.03777059712763, 732.161063095238, 119.56704799697661], "id_box_line": 5, "box_line": [146.41967996031744, 178.65681821617534, 163.0817342261905, 21.948000377928906], "text": "tion environments.", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841714, "box": [146.41967996031744, 207.47764890400606, 732.1428205357142, 41.47185638699921], "id_box_line": 6, "box_line": [146.41967996031744, 207.47764890400606, 732.1428205357142, 21.94800037792902], "text": "Let\u2019s see some of the characteristics of namespaces and how they can help us in differ\u2010", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841714, "box": [146.41967996031744, 207.47764890400606, 732.1428205357142, 41.47185638699921], "id_box_line": 7, "box_line": [146.4349634424603, 227.00150491307636, 115.95311889880952, 21.948000377928906], "text": "ent scenarios:", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841715, "box": [146.4348556547619, 945.5380580498866, 195.64689533730163, 16.70680427059714], "id_box_line": 46, "box_line": [146.4348556547619, 945.5380580498866, 17.82767653769841, 16.70680427059714], "text": "10 ", "category": "Page-footer", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MyriadPro-SemiboldCond", "size": 9}}, {"id_box": 841715, "box": [146.4348556547619, 945.5380580498866, 195.64689533730163, 16.70680427059714], "id_box_line": 47, "box_line": [179.67414543650793, 945.5380580498866, 6.735706150793646, 16.70680427059714], "text": "| ", "category": "Page-footer", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MyriadPro-SemiboldCond", "size": 9}}, {"id_box": 841715, "box": [146.4348556547619, 945.5380580498866, 195.64689533730163, 16.70680427059714], "id_box_line": 48, "box_line": [201.8214648313492, 945.5380580498866, 140.26028616071432, 16.70680427059714], "text": "Chapter 1: Introduction", "category": "Page-footer", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MyriadPro-SemiboldCond", "size": 9}}, {"id_box": 841716, "box": [164.02459186507934, 730.5710045351474, 714.5560901785714, 139.0909814814815], "id_box_line": 38, "box_line": [164.02459186507934, 730.5710045351474, 12.435603025793654, 21.948031368102818], "text": "\u2022", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841716, "box": [164.02459186507934, 730.5710045351474, 714.5560901785714, 139.0909814814815], "id_box_line": 39, "box_line": [181.68776607142857, 730.5710045351474, 696.8774596230159, 21.948031368102818], "text": "ResourceQuotas can also limit the total sum of computing resources we can", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841716, "box": [164.02459186507934, 730.5710045351474, 714.5560901785714, 139.0909814814815], "id_box_line": 40, "box_line": [183.0387547123016, 750.0948450491308, 695.5357854662698, 21.948000377928963], "text": "request in a given namespace. For example, in a cluster with a capacity of 32 GB", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841716, "box": [164.02459186507934, 730.5710045351474, 714.5560901785714, 139.0909814814815], "id_box_line": 41, "box_line": [183.0266214781746, 769.6186700680272, 695.5356756448414, 21.948000377928963], "text": "RAM and 16 cores, it is possible to allocate half of the resources\u201416 GB RAM", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841716, "box": [164.02459186507934, 730.5710045351474, 714.5560901785714, 139.0909814814815], "id_box_line": 42, "box_line": [183.03574479166667, 789.1424795918367, 695.5356837797619, 21.948000377928963], "text": "and 8 cores\u2014for the production namespace, 8 GB RAM and 4 cores for staging", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841716, "box": [164.02459186507934, 730.5710045351474, 714.5560901785714, 139.0909814814815], "id_box_line": 43, "box_line": [183.04493115079364, 808.666351095994, 695.5357508928571, 21.948000377928963], "text": "environment, 4 GB RAM and 2 cores for development, and the same amount for", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841716, "box": [164.02459186507934, 730.5710045351474, 714.5560901785714, 139.0909814814815], "id_box_line": 44, "box_line": [183.03278164682538, 828.1901761148904, 695.5357386904761, 21.948000377928963], "text": "testing namespaces. The ability of imposing resource constraints on a group of", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841716, "box": [164.02459186507934, 730.5710045351474, 714.5560901785714, 139.0909814814815], "id_box_line": 45, "box_line": [183.04195173611112, 847.7139856386999, 541.4562967757936, 21.948000377928935], "text": "objects by using namespaces and ResourceQuotas is invaluable.", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841717, "box": [164.0310306547619, 626.7539066515495, 714.5434485119047, 100.04331594860162], "id_box_line": 32, "box_line": [164.0310306547619, 626.7539066515495, 11.527849603174616, 21.94798488284198], "text": "\u2022", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841717, "box": [164.0310306547619, 626.7539066515495, 714.5434485119047, 100.04331594860162], "id_box_line": 33, "box_line": [180.4048768849206, 626.7539066515495, 698.1604708333332, 21.94798488284198], "text": "ResourceQuotas provide constraints that limit the aggregated resource consump\u2010", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841717, "box": [164.0310306547619, 626.7539066515495, 714.5434485119047, 100.04331594860162], "id_box_line": 34, "box_line": [183.03880148809523, 646.277716175359, 695.5356776785713, 21.948000377928906], "text": "tion per namespace. With ResourceQuotas, a cluster administrator can control", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841717, "box": [164.0310306547619, 626.7539066515495, 714.5434485119047, 100.04331594860162], "id_box_line": 35, "box_line": [183.0266214781746, 665.8015411942554, 695.5357366567459, 21.948000377928963], "text": "the number of objects per type that are allowed in a namespace. For example, a", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841717, "box": [164.0310306547619, 626.7539066515495, 714.5434485119047, 100.04331594860162], "id_box_line": 36, "box_line": [183.03583834325397, 685.3253972033258, 695.5357122519841, 21.948000377928963], "text": "developer namespace may allow only five ConfigMaps, five Secrets, five Services,", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841717, "box": [164.0310306547619, 626.7539066515495, 714.5434485119047, 100.04331594860162], "id_box_line": 37, "box_line": [183.04500843253967, 704.8492222222221, 513.5250813492063, 21.948000377928963], "text": "five ReplicaSets, five PersistentVolumeClaims, and ten Pods.", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841718, "box": [164.0396740079365, 521.0983321995465, 714.5384048611111, 101.88171504157219], "id_box_line": 24, "box_line": [164.0396740079365, 521.0983321995465, 11.791217658730147, 21.948000377928906], "text": "\u2022", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841718, "box": [164.0396740079365, 521.0983321995465, 714.5384048611111, 101.88171504157219], "id_box_line": 25, "box_line": [180.7875821924603, 521.0983321995465, 697.7777045138889, 21.948000377928906], "text": "Each Kubernetes Service belongs to a namespace and gets a corresponding DNS", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841718, "box": [164.0396740079365, 521.0983321995465, 714.5384048611111, 101.88171504157219], "id_box_line": 26, "box_line": [183.03880148809523, 541.5414187452759, 431.8118006944444, 21.948000377928963], "text": "address that has the namespace in the form of ", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841718, "box": [164.0396740079365, 521.0983321995465, 714.5384048611111, 101.88171504157219], "id_box_line": 27, "box_line": [614.8506021825397, 544.8035374149661, 263.72393799603174, 15.456302721088377], "text": "<service-name>.<namespace-", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+UbuntuMono-Regular", "size": 9.975000381469727}}, {"id_box": 841718, "box": [164.0396740079365, 521.0983321995465, 714.5384048611111, 101.88171504157219], "id_box_line": 28, "box_line": [183.03309280753967, 565.2465619803477, 233.29426879960317, 15.456318216175305], "text": "name>.svc.cluster.local", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+UbuntuMono-Regular", "size": 9.975000381469727}}, {"id_box": 841718, "box": [164.0396740079365, 521.0983321995465, 714.5384048611111, 101.88171504157219], "id_box_line": 29, "box_line": [416.3273412698412, 561.9844588057446, 462.24142311507944, 21.948000377928906], "text": ". So the namespace name is in the URI of every Ser\u2010", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841718, "box": [164.0396740079365, 521.0983321995465, 714.5384048611111, 101.88171504157219], "id_box_line": 30, "box_line": [183.04224662698414, 581.5082218442933, 695.5358322420634, 21.948000377928906], "text": "vice belonging to the given namespace. That\u2019s one reason it is vital to name", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841718, "box": [164.0396740079365, 521.0983321995465, 714.5384048611111, 101.88171504157219], "id_box_line": 31, "box_line": [183.03009712301585, 601.0320468631896, 162.59062906746036, 21.948000377928963], "text": "namespaces wisely.", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841719, "box": [164.0338392361111, 475.85266288737716, 714.531447470238, 41.47182539682541], "id_box_line": 21, "box_line": [164.0338392361111, 475.85266288737716, 11.751094196428568, 21.94800037792902], "text": "\u2022", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841719, "box": [164.0338392361111, 475.85266288737716, 714.531447470238, 41.47182539682541], "id_box_line": 22, "box_line": [180.72475823412697, 475.85266288737716, 697.8405284722222, 21.94800037792902], "text": "Some other resources such as namespaces themselves, nodes, and PersistentVo\u2010", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841719, "box": [164.0338392361111, 475.85266288737716, 714.531447470238, 41.47182539682541], "id_box_line": 23, "box_line": [183.0387547123016, 495.3764879062736, 688.1166564980158, 21.948000377928963], "text": "lumes do not belong to namespaces and should have unique cluster-wide names.", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841720, "box": [164.02738417658728, 352.511708994709, 714.5534198908731, 119.56714096749806], "id_box_line": 14, "box_line": [164.02738417658728, 352.511708994709, 12.059710714285728, 21.948000377928906], "text": "\u2022", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841720, "box": [164.02738417658728, 352.511708994709, 714.5534198908731, 119.56714096749806], "id_box_line": 15, "box_line": [181.15666354166666, 352.511708994709, 697.4086841765873, 21.948000377928906], "text": "By default, namespaces provide scope for resources, but nothing isolates those", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841720, "box": [164.02738417658728, 352.511708994709, 714.5534198908731, 119.56714096749806], "id_box_line": 16, "box_line": [183.0387547123016, 372.0354875283447, 695.5358464781744, 21.948046863189802], "text": "resources and prevents access from one resource to another. For example, a Pod", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841720, "box": [164.02738417658728, 352.511708994709, 714.5534198908731, 119.56714096749806], "id_box_line": 17, "box_line": [183.0266214781746, 391.5593590325019, 695.5357366567459, 21.94800037792902], "text": "from a development namespace can access another Pod from a production", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841720, "box": [164.02738417658728, 352.511708994709, 714.5534198908731, 119.56714096749806], "id_box_line": 18, "box_line": [183.03583834325397, 411.08312207105064, 695.5356512400792, 21.94804686318969], "text": "namespace as long as the Pod IP address is known. However, there are Kuber\u2010", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841720, "box": [164.02738417658728, 352.511708994709, 714.5534198908731, 119.56714096749806], "id_box_line": 19, "box_line": [183.0450552083333, 430.60699357520787, 695.535748859127, 21.948000377928906], "text": "netes plugins that provide networking isolation to achieve true multitenancy", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841720, "box": [164.02738417658728, 352.511708994709, 714.5534198908731, 119.56714096749806], "id_box_line": 20, "box_line": [183.03290570436508, 450.1308030990174, 248.4984395337301, 21.94804686318969], "text": "across namespaces if desired.", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841721, "box": [164.0305039186508, 287.7422301587302, 714.5440362599206, 60.99568140589565], "id_box_line": 10, "box_line": [164.0305039186508, 287.7422301587302, 11.818807242063485, 21.94798488284198], "text": "\u2022", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841721, "box": [164.0305039186508, 287.7422301587302, 714.5440362599206, 60.99568140589565], "id_box_line": 11, "box_line": [180.8175898809524, 287.7422301587302, 697.7476968253968, 21.94798488284198], "text": "A namespace provides scope for resources such as containers, Pods, Services, or", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841721, "box": [164.0305039186508, 287.7422301587302, 714.5440362599206, 60.99568140589565], "id_box_line": 12, "box_line": [183.03867743055554, 307.2660396825397, 695.5358627480159, 21.948000377928906], "text": "ReplicaSets. The names of resources need to be unique within a namespace, but", "category": "List-item", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/CPDGGC+MinionPro-Regular", "size": 10.5}}, {"id_box": 841721, "box": [164.0305039186508, 287.7422301587302, 714.5440362599206, 60.99568140589565], "id_box_line": 13, "box_line": [183.0264974206349, 326.789864701436